[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0216","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0216.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0674","title":"BSD 系列操作系统 profil 系统调用本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统 profil(2) 系统调用存在安全缺陷，本地攻击者可通过 profile 与 execve 的组合调用，在程序执行过程中修改其内部数据空间，进而导致进程行为异常或权限提升。此漏洞影响 NetBSD 1.4、OpenBSD 2.5 及 Solaris 7.0 等多个 Unix 类操作系统，攻击者需具备本地用户账户权限才能利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0674"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.237","remediation":"NetBSD 用户应升级至 1.4.1 及以上版本，OpenBSD 用户应升级至 2.6 及以上版本，Solaris 用户应安装对应操作系统补丁包或升级至 Solaris 8/9，以修复 profil(2) 系统调用中关于 profiling 与 execve 的内部数据空间修改问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-067.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/570","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19447","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0674.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0674","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0674.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0674.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q8cp-g8hf-5jjj/GHSA-q8cp-g8hf-5jjj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0674.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0216.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0409","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0409.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0722","title":"Cobalt RaQ2 默认配置远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Cobalt RaQ2 服务器默认配置存在安全缺陷，未对远程用户的软件包安装权限进行有效限制。攻击者无需身份认证即可通过默认开放的远程管理接口向服务器安装任意软件包，进而获得服务器的完全控制权。该漏洞严重影响所有采用默认配置的 Cobalt RaQ2 设备，可导致数据泄露、服务中断等严重后果。建议管理员立即修改默认配置并限制远程访问权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0722"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.193","remediation":"立即登录 Cobalt RaQ2 管理控制台，在 \"System Administration > Remote Package Installation\" 中取消勾选 \"Allow remote installation\"，然后应用保存。在防火墙层面，限制对 TCP 81 端口（管理界面）的访问来源仅为受信任的管理 IP 段。由于该产品已停止维护，建议将服务迁移至受支持的 Linux 发行版（如 CentOS/RHEL 替代方案）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/558"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0409.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0322","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0322.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0727","title":"OpenBSD 内核 IPsec 数据加密绕过漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 内核存在信息泄露漏洞，由于内核在处理 IPsec 加密时未正确管理内存或密钥数据，导致部分 IPsec 数据包可能以明文形式发送。远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探方式捕获这些未加密的数据包，获取其中的敏感通信内容，破坏 IPsec 本应提供的机密性保护。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0727"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.840","remediation":"立即下载 OpenBSD 官方补丁 009_ipsec_in_use.patch（位于 ftp.openbsd.org/pub/OpenBSD/patches/2.5/common/），执行 cd /usr/src && patch -p0 < 009_ipsec_in_use.patch 后重新编译内核。或直接升级至 OpenBSD 2.6 及以上版本，该版本已合入此修复。如无法立即升级，建议在关键网关上禁用 IPsec 隧道或限制对 IPsec SA 管理接口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6127"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0322.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0239","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0682","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 SMTP 邮件中继安全绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 存在电子邮件中继绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可以利用封装的 SMTP 地址格式（如\"<user@domain.com>\"嵌入在邮件地址字段中）发送邮件，即使服务器已启用防中继功能，仍能绕过限制将邮件中继到外部域。该漏洞可被垃圾邮件发送者利用来发送大量垃圾邮件，导致服务器被滥用为开放中继。影响 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 版本，攻击无需认证，仅需构造特制邮件地址即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0682"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.280","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-027 提供的 Exchange Server 5.5 安全更新，该补丁使封装的 SMTP 地址同样受反中继保护。若无法安装补丁，可在 Internet Mail Service 属性中将中继权限限制为仅允许经过身份验证的用户，并禁用不必要的站点到站点 SMTP 中继功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237927","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-056.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/567","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-027"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0319","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0319.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0719","title":"GNOME Gnumeric Guile 插件代码执行漏洞","description":"Gnumeric 电子表格软件中的 Guile 插件存在代码执行漏洞。攻击者可通过构造恶意的电子表格文件，诱使用户在受影响版本中打开该文件，从而触发该漏洞并执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Gnumeric 的受影响版本，攻击复杂度较高，需要用户交互配合，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0719"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.830","remediation":"升级至 Gnumeric 0.50 及以上版本，该版本已移除存在安全风险的 Guile 插件扩展支持。对于无法升级的系统，直接删除或禁用 Guile 插件文件（如 gnumeric-guile.so），并移除 gnumeric 对 libguile 的依赖调用，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/563"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0319.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0285","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0285.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0703","title":"OpenBSD/BSDI等多款Unix操作系统设备文件标志设置漏洞","description":"OpenBSD、BSDI 及其他类 Unix 操作系统中，普通用户可对字符设备和块设备调用 chflags 及 fchflags 系统调用来修改文件标志位。该漏洞源于内核未对设备特殊文件的标志修改操作进行充分的权限检查，导致低权限用户能够更改设备文件的不可变标志（如 schg、sappnd），从而绕过系统安全策略。攻击者利用此漏洞可修改关键设备文件的保护属性，进而实现文件篡改或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD、BSDI 等多款 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 3.6，危害等级低，攻击需本地用户权限。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0703"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.917","remediation":"升级 OpenBSD 至 2.5 或更高版本，BSDI 升级至 4.0.1 或更高版本，该漏洞已在对应版本的内核中修复了对字符设备和块设备的 chflags/fchflags 权限检查。如无法升级，可通过限制用户对 /dev 目录下设备文件的写入权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-066.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0703.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0703","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0703.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0703.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r2hm-7w9p-5qrc/GHSA-r2hm-7w9p-5qrc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0703.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--397c3002-48f0-4b72-a230-03cbb311dac0.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000716.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0285.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0204","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0671","title":"ToxSoft NextFTP 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ToxSoft NextFTP 1.82 客户端存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务器发送特制的 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令触发该漏洞，导致目标系统上的 NextFTP 客户端程序崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 NextFTP 1.82 版本，攻击者需诱骗用户连接至恶意 FTP 服务器，利用难度中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0671"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.857","remediation":"ToxSoft 已停止运营，官方未发布补丁。建议立即停止使用 NextFTP 1.82，迁移至仍受维护的 FTP 客户端（如 FileZilla、WinSCP）。如暂时无法替换，可通过网络防火墙或 IPS 规则拦截包含超长 CWD 命令的 FTP 请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/572","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19448","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0671.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0671","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0671.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0671.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/308.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0671.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.224","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0211","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0672","title":"Fujitsu Chocoa IRC 客户端 Topic 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Fujitsu Chocoa IRC 客户端在处理 IRC 频道主题（Topic）时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向运行该客户端的用户发送特制的畸形频道主题数据，触发缓冲区溢出，导致客户端崩溃或可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R 版本，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0672"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.990","remediation":"Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R 已停止维护，官方未发布修复版本。建议立即停止使用该客户端，迁移至仍在维护的 IRC 客户端（如 mIRC、HexChat、Irssi）。作为临时缓解措施，可在 IRC 服务器端或客户端配置中过滤/禁用自动解析频道主题，避免触发缓冲区溢出。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/573","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19449","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0672","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0672.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/307.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.223","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1014","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1227","title":"Ethereal 数据包捕获文件本地符号链接攻击任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Ethereal（现更名为 Wireshark）网络封包分析工具在保存捕获文件时未能正确处理符号链接（symlink），存在不安全的临时文件释放漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在目标系统上预设恶意的符号链接，诱使 Ethereal 进程将捕获数据写入攻击者指定的任意文件路径，从而覆盖系统关键文件或用户数据。该漏洞攻击条件简单，本地用户即可利用，影响所有使用 Ethereal 保存数据包捕获文件的场景，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1227"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.377","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 Ethereal 在写入数据包捕获文件时未检查符号链接，攻击者可提前创建指向任意系统文件的符号链接，诱使 Ethereal 覆盖目标文件。建议立即升级至 Ethereal 0.8.0 或更高版本（该版本已修复符号链接跟随问题），或直接迁移至 Wireshark（Ethereal 的更名后继项目，默认不存在此漏洞）。临时缓解措施：避免以 root 权限运行 Ethereal，将捕获文件输出到专用目录并确保该目录不允许非信任用户写入，同时设置严格的 umask 限制文件权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ethereal.com/lists/ethereal-dev/199907/msg00126.html","http://www.ethereal.com/lists/ethereal-dev/199907/msg00130.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3334","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1227","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1227.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fx42-9wp5-842h/GHSA-fx42-9wp5-842h.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87548/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000713.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0972","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1130","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server JHTML 文件源码泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1及3.6版本中搜索引擎的默认配置存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过构造特制的搜索请求，利用HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat模式文件读取服务器上JHTML文件的源代码，导致敏感信息（如数据库连接参数、业务逻辑配置等）泄露。该漏洞影响Netscape Enterprise Server多个版本，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1130"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.070","remediation":"Netscape Enterprise Server 已停止维护且不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 IIS）。作为临时缓解措施，可删除或重命名默认搜索配置中的 HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat 模式文件，并限制对搜索功能的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93346448121208&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93337389603117&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/559","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19443"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0972.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0240","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0240.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0683","title":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 ICMP Packet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 在处理异常格式的 ICMP 数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标防火墙发送特制的畸形 ICMP 报文，触发异常的报文处理流程，导致防火墙服务崩溃或停止响应，从而阻断正常网络流量通过。该漏洞直接影响 Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0683"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.410","remediation":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 已停止技术支持，官方不再发布安全补丁。建议立即升级至仍在支持周期内的现代防火墙产品。如需临时缓解，可在网络边界 ACL 中配置丢弃畸形 ICMP 报文（如分片 ICMP、长度异常 ICMP 等），并限制 ICMP 速率，减少拒绝服务攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1029","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/556","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19441","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0683.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-