Check Point Firewall-1 至 4.1 及以上版本，该版本修复了非 SYN 包长超时问题，引入了正确的 TCP 状态跟踪机制。如无法升级，可在防火墙上手动调低非 SYN 连接的超时阈值，并限制单源 IP 的并发连接数，同时部署 ingress 过滤以阻断伪造源地址的攻击流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1027","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/549","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19436"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0492.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0276","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0276.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0700","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Phone Dialer 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 Phone Dialer（dialer.exe）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向 dialer.ini 配置文件写入特制的畸形拨号条目，在程序解析该条目时触发缓冲区溢出，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及所有 Service Pack 版本，攻击者需具备本地或远程写入 dialer.ini 文件的能力。成功利用后可获取目标系统控制权。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0700"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.550","remediation":"升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 或安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-037 提供的补丁。如无法升级，通过 NTFS 权限限制 dialer.ini 文件仅允许 Administrators 组写入，并移除 dialer.exe 的 Everyone 执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237185","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-026","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19440","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0700","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0700.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0700.json","https: